Artra Group unit completes acquisition . Artra Group Inc said Monday its Bagcraft Corp of America unit completed the purchase of AB Specialty Holding Co from Stone Container Corp . Terms were not disclosed . In mid - December , Artra completed the acquisition of the Alfred J . Bleyer Bag Division from the Fonda Group . " Together , those two niche acquisitions will add approximately 10 percent to Bagcraft ' s annual sales base and have ( a ) positive effect on earnings , " Mark Santacrose , Bagcraft president , said in a statement . Bagcraft , with annual sales of about $ 130 million , makes flexible packaging . ( ( Reuters Chicago Newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
